<HEADLINE>
<P>
FREEWAY REPAIRS; 
</P>
<P>
ON THE ROAD; 
</P>
<P>
CALTRANS ISSUES ADVISORY ON THIS WEEK'S REPAIR SITES SO MOTORISTS CAN STEER 
CLEAR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Caltrans advises motorists that it plans the following freeway work in the 
Southeast and Long Beach area this week. Repair locations listed below are 
keyed to the nearest city or cities and are spotted on the map by number. 
</P>
<P>
ARTESIA FREEWAY (91) 
</P>
<P>
1. Bellflower /Cerritos: Eastbound No. 1 diamond lane; Woodruff Avenue to San 
Gabriel River Freeway (605); Tuesday, 8:30 a.m. to 1 p.m.; landscaping. 
</P>
<P>
2. Bellflower /Cerritos: Eastbound No. 6 lane; Woodruff Avenue to San Gabriel 
River Freeway (605); Wednesday, 8:30 a.m. to 1 p.m.; shoulder repair. 
</P>
<P>
HARBOR FREEWAY (110) 
</P>
<P>
3. San Pedro: Northbound No. 1 lane; Gaffey Street to Channel Street; Monday, 8 
a.m. to 2 p.m.; raised markers. 
</P>
<P>
4. San Pedro: Southbound alternating lanes; Channel Street to Gaffey Street; 
Tuesday, 9:30 a.m. to 2:30 p.m.; raised markers. 
</P>
<P>
5. San Pedro: Westbound No. 3 lane, Harbor Boulevard to Terminal Island 
separation, Harbor Boulevard on-ramp and westbound Terminal Island connector to 
northbound Harbor Freeway (110); Wednesday, 9:30 a.m. to 2:30 p.m.; raised 
markers. 
</P>
<P>
LONG BEACH FREEWAY (710) 
</P>
<P>
6. South Gate: Southbound No. 4 lane; Firestone Boulevard to Los Angeles River; 
Friday, 9:30 a.m. to 2:30 p.m.; guardrail repair. 
</P>
<P>
SAN GABRIEL RIVER FREEWAY (605) 
</P>
<P>
7. Pico Rivera / Whittier: Southbound No. 3 and 4 lanes; Peck Road to Whittier 
Boulevard; today, 6 a.m. to noon; raised markers. 
</P>
<P>
8. Pico Rivera /Whittier: Northbound No. 1 lane; Washington Boulevard to 
Beverly Boulevard; Monday, 9:30 a.m. to 2:30 p.m.; raised markers. 
</P>
<P>
9. Pico Rivera / Whittier: Northbound No. 1 lane; Beverly Boulevard to Peck 
Road; Tuesday, 9:30 a.m. to 2:30 p.m.; raised markers. 
</P>
<P>
10. Santa Fe Springs: Northbound No. 3 lane; at Florence Avenue and Florence 
Avenue on-ramp; today, 7 to 11 a.m.; bridge repair. 
</P>
<P>
SANTA ANA FREEWAY (5) 
</P>
<P>
11. Downey: Southbound shoulder at the northbound Lakewood Boulevard on-ramp; 
Wednesday, 8:30 a.m. to 1 p.m.; landscaping. 
</P>
<P>
12. La Mirada: Northbound No. 4 lane; Artesia Boulevard to Rosecrans Avenue; 
Thursday, 8:30 a.m. to 1:30 p.m.; landscaping. 
</P>
<P>
13. Norwalk: Northbound ramps; westbound Norwalk Boulevard and Imperial Avenue 
off-ramp; Monday, 8 a.m. to 2 p.m.; landscaping. 
</P>
<P>
14. Santa Fe Springs: Northbound and southbound No. 1 lanes; Alondra Boulevard 
to Valley View Avenue; today, 5:30 a.m. to 1 p.m.; guardrail repair. 
</P>
<P>
TERMINAL ISLAND FREEWAY (103) 
</P>
<P>
15. Long Beach: Northbound all lanes; Anaheim Street to Pacific Coast Highway, 
Anaheim Street on-ramp, Pacific Coast Highway off-ramp and on-ramp; detour 
northbound Terminal Island Freeway (103) traffic from Anaheim Street to Pacific 
Coast Highway; Monday, 8 a.m. to 2 p.m.; bridge repair. 
</P>
<P>
16. Long Beach: Northbound No. 1 lane; Seaside Avenue to Anaheim Street; 
Thursday, 9:30 a.m. to 2:30 p.m.; raised markers. 
</P>
</TEXT>
